very large glass of wine, please.

34:15.467 --> 34:18.190
Is this color peach or salmon?

34:18.208 --> 34:20.552
Marc! Marc, will you cover 
my phones for me, please?

34:20.567 --> 34:23.152
- Daniel forgot the proposal--
- Oh, I'll bring it to the restaurant.

34:23.187 --> 34:24.630
No, I'll take it to him.
It's my job.

34:24.668 --> 34:27.612
Oh, come on. They won't even let
you past the host at Madison Six.

34:27.628 --> 34:29.810
Ah-ah. Just let me. I got it.

34:29.826 --> 34:31.962
Marc, give it to me!

34:31.978 --> 34:33.739
I can't hit your boss,
but I can hit you.

34:33.757 --> 34:37.051
And everybody knows I'm from Queens,
so I will do it!

34:38.255 --> 34:39.821
Thank you.

34:45.097 --> 34:47.491
So none of the girls
looked like you

34:47.505 --> 34:50.061
when I went to
Queensborough High.

34:50.338 --> 34:54.192
Hey, does Mrs.
Rodriguez still teach there?

34:54.206 --> 34:57.139
I'm gonna say...

34:58.338 --> 34:59.861
she died.

35:11.825 --> 35:17.202
So you're still just
a creative director?

35:17.936 --> 35:20.162
Yes, daddy.

35:21.096 --> 35:22.790
Shall we?

35:29.428 --> 35:32.232
So, uh, we feel 
this holiday issue is our chance

35:32.247 --> 35:35.513
to try something really out
there for our feature spread.

35:35.526 --> 35:38.851
4-page pullout. You would have
total carte blanche, of course.

35:38.866 --> 35:41.321
So what does your
old man do, anyway?

35:41.336 --> 35:43.632
Investment banker.

35:43.927 --> 35:46.792
Your father's an investment
banker... Betty?

35:46.805 --> 35:51.190
Oh. I mean, yeah.
That was always his dream.

35:51.206 --> 35:55.252
You know, if he ever 
made it out of the Bare-Rio.

35:55.266 --> 35:56.650
What?

35:56.665 --> 35:59.200
- Okay, that it's it. It's over.
- Daniel...

35:59.218 --> 36:01.413
Look, I can't keep
doing this, dad.

36:01.427 --> 36:03.190
I'm sorry, Mr. Bianchi.

36:03.207 --> 36:04.342
Are you ready to
hear the specials?

36:04.375 --> 36:05.760
Actually, could you hold
off on the specials?

36:05.797 --> 36:09.263
I'm about to blow a very,
uh, big deal here.

36:09.276 --> 36:11.273
Mr. Bianchi...

36:11.286 --> 36:13.992
this is not Betty Suarez.

36:14.236 --> 36:15.962
Hmm?

36:19.425 --> 36:20.770
No kidding.

36:20.785 --> 36:22.643
Come on. Give me some credit.

36:22.656 --> 36:26.261
This girl's never been within 10 feet of
a sausage and pepper hero in her life.

36:26.277 --> 36:28.023
He is so right.

36:28.036 --> 36:30.012
So where's the girl I
talked to on the phone?

36:30.026 --> 36:31.342
She didn't want to come,

36:31.358 --> 36:32.941
and it's my fault.

36:32.957 --> 36:35.181
And she was looking forward
to meeting you very much.

36:35.198 --> 36:38.921
But because we're all caught
up with some stupid image,

36:38.938 --> 36:41.803
I made her feel insecure about
fitting into a place like this.

36:41.816 --> 36:44.731
He's my boss. I just need to--I
need to take him the envelope.

36:44.747 --> 36:46.591
He's right there.
It's just 10 feet in.

36:46.608 --> 36:49.660
I can't imagine why you
thought she wouldn't fit in.

36:50.348 --> 36:52.113
Look, here he comes.
He'll tell you.

36:52.126 --> 36:54.601
I'm so sorry, Mr. Meade.
She says that she's with you.

36:54.615 --> 36:55.781
She is.

36:55.796 --> 36:57.980
Look, sir. You just--you
forgot the layout proposal.

36:57.998 --> 37:00.011
There's someone I want you to meet.
Come here.

37:03.815 --> 37:06.541
Now this must be Betty Suarez.

37:06.557 --> 37:09.041
Mr. Bianchi. Hi.

37:09.056 --> 37:10.761
It's really an honor.

37:10.777 --> 37:12.232
Really.

37:12.247 --> 37:14.250
Look, Mr. Bianchi,

37:14.266 --> 37:17.592
between your fight with my brother and
what we just tried to pull off here,

37:17.608 --> 37:19.813
I'm sure there isn't a reason in
hell you'd want to work with us,

37:19.846 --> 37:22.561
but I gotta say, I--

37:22.578 --> 37:25.253
I think it'd be a great
opportunity for both of us.

37:25.267 --> 37:27.593
You would have free rein
to call your own shots.

37:27.605 --> 37:28.722
I give you my word.

37:28.737 --> 37:31.613
Actually, I give
you Betty's word.

37:31.627 --> 37:34.741
She's the only one who's been
straight with you so far.

37:39.347 --> 37:41.812
You know,
you're nothing like your brother.

37:41.825 --> 37:44.992
No. I'm not.

37:46.518 --> 37:48.580
I'm not Alex.

37:49.848 --> 37:52.052
I'll leave you
with the proposal.

37:52.065 --> 37:54.032
Mr. Bianchi.

37:56.677 --> 37:58.631
Here you go.

37:58.746 --> 38:00.440
Thanks.

38:07.406 --> 38:10.351
Excuse me.
Could I get a matchbook, please?

38:10.365 --> 38:12.860
My nephew is never
gonna believe this.

38:12.875 --> 38:14.541
Awesome. Thanks.

38:19.875 --> 38:22.263
I just wanted to say I'm sorry.

38:22.278 --> 38:25.381
I should have insisted you
come to lunch with me today.

38:25.478 --> 38:28.272
Well, Daniel,
I'm sorry that I backed down.

38:28.287 --> 38:31.741
I mean, I should not have let
Wilhelmina get to me like that.

38:31.755 --> 38:34.620
Look, fake nails or not,
you came through for us, Betty.

38:34.635 --> 38:36.722
Bianchi was only
there because of you.

38:36.737 --> 38:39.953
I guess you really do
have cojones, huh?

38:41.556 --> 38:43.623
So I'm going to go.

38:48.117 --> 38:50.311
- He's doing it.
- We got him?

38:50.325 --> 38:51.601
We got him.

38:51.615 --> 38:54.681
His one stipulation is that
he answers only to you

38:54.697 --> 38:58.002
and to no other "blowhards."

38:58.016 --> 38:59.832
Okay.

39:01.558 --> 39:06.380
Betty, uh, please send 
an e-mail to all creative.

39:06.396 --> 39:10.932
"Vincent Bianchi will be shooting
our december feature spread."

39:10.948 --> 39:13.233
Shut up!

39:13.408 --> 39:15.523
Right away, sir.

39:17.206 --> 39:19.172
Congratulations.

39:19.186 --> 39:21.031
Thank you.

39:23.335 --> 39:28.203
Dad, I got a weird
call from some woman.

39:28.217 --> 39:32.063
She said to ask you about
Bayonne scrape yard.

39:32.366 --> 39:34.433
Mean anything?

39:34.448 --> 39:36.472
I haven't the foggiest.

39:36.488 --> 39:39.380
Must be some kind of crank.

39:39.398 --> 39:42.953
I've never even
been to Bayonne.

39:59.015 --> 40:03.052
Vincent Bianchi will
be shooting december?

40:03.068 --> 40:04.963
He got him?

40:04.975 --> 40:06.543
Damn!

40:32.638 --> 40:35.581
Hey, look who's home
in time for dinner.

40:35.595 --> 40:37.482
What happened to your makeup

40:37.497 --> 40:39.242
and your nails?

40:39.255 --> 40:40.730
It was kind a long day.

40:40.747 --> 40:41.993
They didn't fire you, did they?

40:42.007 --> 40:43.191
'Cause I'll go down there.

40:43.207 --> 40:45.780
No, dad, they didn't fire me.

40:45.796 --> 40:48.960
In fact, because of me,

40:48.977 --> 40:52.472
we landed Vincent Bianchi
for a big magazine shoot.

40:52.487 --> 40:54.042
That's a big deal?

40:54.057 --> 40:55.462
I could've gotten you that kid.

40:55.475 --> 40:58.010
Yes, dad,
it's kind of a big deal.

40:58.025 --> 41:01.310
It's a really big deal.

41:01.325 --> 41:03.803
Well, in that case...

41:05.097 --> 41:06.720
I'm very proud of you.

41:06.737 --> 41:08.500
Thank you.

41:12.507 --> 41:13.911
And you know what?

41:13.927 --> 41:15.720
If it wasn't for
Hilda's makeover,

41:15.738 --> 41:17.841
